  <section id="description" class="rel-mt-2 rich-input-content" aria-label="Record description">
    <h2 id="description-heading" class="sr-only">Description</h2>
    
    <div style="word-wrap: break-word;">
      <p>Geographical clustering of the earliest known COVID-19 cases and the proximity of positive environmental samples to live-animal vendors suggest that the Huanan Seafood Wholesale Market in Wuhan was the site of origin of the COVID-19 pandemic.</p>
    </div>
  </section>



  
    
    
